overview: Masseuse Cadence Lux indulges her client T. Stone's fantasy by wearing a wet dress throughout his massage. Betrayed wife Rachel Roxxx gets her revenge by massaging her husband's brother Aaron Wilcox at his favorite spa. Masseuse Val Dodds impresses her new client Olivia Austin with a sensual first-time experience. Masseuse Zoey Monroe pampers her boyfriend Marcus London with a slippery massage after he ruins his t-shirt. Spa receptionist Ana Foxx assists masseuse Kate England proving teamwork is best for the client Xander Corvus.
title: Oops I Spilled!
